dct_description_sm: Geological Survey of New Jersey. Atlas Sheet 21 (1906) New Jersey Geological Survey Relief show by 20 ft. contour intervals and spot heights. Title was not given. Region covered: Kittatinny Valley and Mountain. Original survey 1880 and 1883, principal features revised 1906.
